      "role": "user",
      "content": "yea i'm sitting in the shade now but the talking part is still really weird. like i know what i want to say but the words just dont come out right its like my brain is lagging. i already drank a whole bottle of water but im still feeling pretty out of it. do you think i should just take some electrolytes and sleep it off? i really dont want to go to a hospital if i can help it, it seems like way too much for just being in the sun.",
