      "content": "i dont really wanna deal with a clinic right now lol. i just want to fix this so i can get back to my hotel. if i just take a bunch of electrolyte powder and some more water, won't that fix the brain fog stuff? i feel like i'm just a bit overheated and my electrolytes are just low. is it safe to just double up on the electrolytes so i can sleep it off?",
